## Configuration

### ❌ NEVER do this:
```python
API_KEY = "sk-1234567890"  # Hardcoded secret!
DATABASE_URL = "sqlite:///./prod.db"  # Hardcoded path
```

### ✅ ALWAYS do this:
```python
from pydantic_settings import BaseSettings

class Settings(BaseSettings):
    api_key: str  # Required from environment
    database_url: str = "sqlite:///./dev.db"  # Default for dev only
    
    class Config:
        env_file = ".env"
```

