## Async/Sync Consistency

This project uses **synchronous** database operations with SQLModel.

### ❌ NEVER do this:
```python
# Mixing async/sync
@router.get("/")
async def get_items(session: Session = Depends(get_session)):
    # This blocks the event loop!
    items = session.exec(select(Item)).all()
    return items
```

### ✅ ALWAYS do this:
```python
# Stay synchronous
@router.get("/")
def get_items(session: Session = Depends(get_session)):
    items = session.exec(select(Item)).all()
    return items
```

